SELECT   a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/value as T0_dv_text,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0005]/value as T0_dv_coded_text
        FROM EHR e CONTAINS COMPOSITION c
            CONTAINS (OBSERVATION a[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.supported_data_types.v0])
 LIMIT 1
        ORDER BY c /context/start_time/ value DESC
